  "comment": "Dalis 864 footlight: Dalis 864 Footlight is a new 150W colour\nvariation of the original Dalis 862 tuneable white footlight, designed for the creation of colourful upstage or\ndownstage lighting. Featuring a 4-colour mixing system, it incorporates 48 patented asymmetric reflectors arranged\nin a double row, independently controlled. The Footlight batten is inconspicuous from the audience viewpoint to\nensure it does not impinge on the stage layout. All controls and connections are located under the unit to maintain\nclean sight lines. Each unit also integrates four discreet red and blue ‘mark’ LEDs. They can be used as position\nmarkers or cue lights for the performers on stage, and also as safety indicators to mark the edge of the stage.",
